item.title: CVE-2023-1436|2024-08-02T05:49:11.438Z -- jettison -- jettison
item.description: An infinite recursion is triggered in Jettison when constructing a JSONArray from a Collection that contains a self-reference in one of its elements. This leads to a StackOverflowError exception being thrown.
